BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:K8H4aMs-x8E54rXNRe2r2
SUMMARY:Glenn's Last Ride Acoustic Tour: Logan Mize w/ Keelan Donovan
DTSTAMP:20260308T025026Z
DTSTART:20260415T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Ten years ago before earning gold records\, Logan toured in his
	 89 station wagon named Glenn and developed a devoted following of fans ac
	ross the country that loved his unique and relatable experience of crowd-s
	ourced touring. This spring as an homage to how Logan toured in his statio
	n wagon\, weve rebooted the Glenn tour for one last ride. Over his nearly 
	two-decade career\, Logan has risen as a top independent artist\, bending 
	the country genre with his unique heartland rock sound and racking up over
	 500 million streams. Hes shared the stage with legendary acts including E
	ric Church\, Jamey Johnson\, Sawyer Brown\, Wade Bowen and many more. Loga
	ns singles Better Off Gone and Grew Apart have both earned RIAA Gold certi
	fication. Logans next full-length record Cottonwood Falls will be released
	 this spring.\nThis event is 21 and over. Any ticket holder unable to pres
	ent valid identification indicating that they are at least 21 years of age
	 will not be admitted to this event\, and will not be eligible for a refun
	d. This ticket is for admission to a live music venue. It provides the hol
	der to observe a musical performance and nothing else. Other goods and ser
	vices may be purchased once inside the venue. Please note\, seating is lim
	ited and is available on a first come\, first served basis.\nPrice: $25.08
	 - $25.08\n\nhttps://www.ticketweb.com/event/glenns-last-ride-acoustic-tou
	r-tractor-tickets/14120304\n\nFrom Tractor Tavern
URL:https://www.ticketweb.com/event/glenns-last-ride-acoustic-tour-tractor-
	tickets/14120304
LOCATION:Tractor\, 5213 Ballard Avenue NW\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:tractor-tavern
CATEGORIES:Tractor Tavern
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
